    "overview": {
      "title": "What is Glossa?",
      "p1": "Glossa is a multi-stage AI translation pipeline designed for scholars, philologists, and professional translators. Instead of a single-shot translation, it chains multiple LLM passes — each with its own instructions and model — to iteratively refine the output.",
      "p2": "An AI judge then audits the final translation against your glossary and quality criteria, assigning a semantic quality label and listing specific issues with suggested fixes.",
