      "step1": "Paste or import your source text",
      "step2": "Text passes through Stage 1 (initial draft)",
      "step3": "Stage 2+ refine the translation (fluency, register, etc.)",
      "step4": "AI Judge audits: quality label, issues, suggested fixes",
      "step5": "You edit the candidate translation manually",
      "step6": "Export as .txt or bilingual .md",
      "p3": "Each stage can use a different model and provider. For example, use Gemini for a fast initial draft, then Claude for stylistic refinement, and GPT-4o as the judge. Or run everything locally with Ollama."
